data.subject: Jingle Bells (Remastered)
data.lyric:
Jingle Bells
 Jingle Bells
 Jingle all the way
 Oh what fun it is to ride
 In a one horse open sleig

data.subject: Something`s Gotta Give
data.lyric:
When an irresistible force
 Such as you
 Meets an old immovable object like me
 You can bet as sure
